data.title: Learn Objective-c Skills & Techniques – Objective-c Tutorial Videos & Training at macProVideo.com
data.meta_description: Learn Objective-c skills by watching tutorial videos about What's New in Final Cut Pro 10.8, Ableton Live Playback Engineering,  Introducing Logic Pro 11, 10 Top Secret Bitwig Tips and Tricks, Cubase 13 Beginners Guide, & more ...
data.text:
Final Cut Pro 10.8 100

What's New in Final Cut Pro 10.8

Final Cut Pro 10.8 introduces a range of new features and improvements to enhance your video editing experience. In this course, veteran video editor Iain Anderson guides you through these updates, equipping you with the skills needed to improve your workflow and create stunning videos.

Ableton Live 12 401

Ableton Live Playback Engineering

Master the art of playback engineering with Ableton Live 12 in this comprehensive course by Rishabh Rajan. Learn how to streamline your live performances, optimize your workflow, and manage complex set lists. Perfect for live sound engineers, musicians, and producers, this course covers everything you need to know to deliver flawless playback performances.

Logic Pro 11 100

Introducing Logic Pro 11

Apple's Logic Pro 11 has dropped, and legendary Logic expert Steve Horelick is here with an exciting, in-depth course. Discover all the new features such as ChromaGlow, Studio Piano, Studio Bass, Stem Splitter, and much more. So learn Logic Pro 11 now with this comprehensive guide.

Bitwig Studio 405

10 Top Secret Bitwig Tips and Tricks

Bitwig Certified Trainer Thavius Beck is back with another course... Join him as he shares his top ten favorite tips and tricks that will change the way you approach your own music and productions.

Ableton Live 12 101

Live 12 Absolute Beginners Guide

Get hands-on with Ableton Live 12 with this comprehensive course by certified trainer Thavius Beck! Spanning over three hours, it's the full guide to the ins and outs of the most advanced version of Live yet. Let's learn!

Serato Sample 101

Learn Serato Sample

Serato Sample is a state-of-the-art plugin with stem separation that lets you manipulate samples from any audio source. Discover how to use Serato Sample to create original and exciting music, with this course by trainer and producer Booker Edwards. Take your sample game to the next level!

Pro Tools 301

Designing Sci-Fi and Futuristic Sound FX

Blast into the future with Pro Tools' mind-bending tools and plugins! Buckle up with commander Alex Hollingsworth in this turbocharged 21-tutorial course, and get ready to decode the secrets of sci-fi sound design and transport your projects beyond the frontiers of tomorrow!

Teenage Engineering EP133 KO II 101

EP133 KO II Sampling Smackdown!

The EP-133 K.O.II is a fascinating and affordable sampler by Swedish company Teenage Engineering. Get ready to "float like a butterfly" and master the EP-133 K.O.II with this knockout guide by music producer Rishabh Rajan!

Plasmonic 101

Plasmonic Explored

Rhizomatic Plasmonic is a unique synth created by the original mind behind the legendary NI Absynth. Explore the intricate acoustic resonances of physical modeling, learn to blend them with subtractive synthesis, and discover new sound creation techniques in this course, with sound designer Rishabh Rajan.

Final Cut 100

What's New in Final Cut 10.7

Apple's Final Cut Pro 10.7 is here and so is Certified Trainer Iain Anderson with this FREE What's New course. These new features will definitely enhance your editing workflow. So dive in and see What's New in Final Cut 10.7

Logic Pro 303

Mastering Assistant In Action

Enhance your mastering skills with Logic Pro's new Mastering Assistant plugin, designed to add that final professional polish on your music projects. Learn to optimize this powerful Apple plugin and ensure your projects sound their absolute best, in this course with mastering engineer Olav Basoski.

Ableton Push 3 101

Push 3 Explored

Unleash your creativity with Ableton's Push 3! Whether you use it as a standalone instrument or paired with a computer, dive into its full potential with this hands-on course led by Ableton Certified Trainer Thavius Beck. Learn Push 3 now!

Logic Pro 100

What’s New In Logic 10.8

Apple's Logic Pro 10.8 is here and it's a FREE upgrade at the App Store. And, here's our What's New in Logic 10.8 course by our own Logic expert Steve H! Check out the 3 brand new plugins, new tools, improved and enhanced workflows and so much more. So, dive in and see What's New!

Groove Guru 201

Creating Grooves

Let's take a groovy trip into the amazing world of rhythm with none other than the Groove Guru himself, Yogev Gabay! Building upon the solid foundation laid down in his previous course, these entertaining lessons will launch your groove game into the stratosphere!

Transit 101- Transit Explored

Transit Explored

Baby Audio and YouTuber Andrew Huang teamed up to create Transit—an innovative multi-effect plugin specifically designed for creating complex transition FX with the twist of a knob. Dive deep into Transit with house producer Olav Basoski, and discover the power that this plugin has to offer.

Ableton Live 408

Live Performance Looping Techniques

Ableton Live is a powerful DAW, but did you know it's also a live looping powerhouse? It IS, and you can learn all about it with Rishabh Rajan this 20 tutorial course!

DaVinci Resolve 101

DaVinci Resolve Essential Beginners Guide

Are you ready to dive into the world of video editing with DaVinci Resolve? Join instructor and video editor Kevin P. McAuliffe in this Essential Beginner's Guide Course, to get the comprehensive skills you need to edit videos like a pro!

Final Cut Pro 100

What's New in Final Cut Pro 10.6.6

Final Cut Pro 10.6.6 brings along an array of new features and enhancements to make your workflow easier. Discover them all in this FREE course, with Final Cut expert Iain Anderson.

Final Cut Pro for iPad - 100

Introducing Final Cut Pro for iPad

Apple's Final Cut Pro for iPad is like having a complete pro video studio at your fingertips! Explore the new touch-based interface, and learn the essential tools and techniques you need to craft stunning videos in this FREE course by Iain Anderson.

FabFilter 301

FabFilter: In The Mix

FabFilter produces a wide range of high-quality mixing plugins to cover all your mixing and mastering needs. Watch this course by house producer Olav Basoski as he takes you through the process of mixing a house music project using only FabFilter plugins!

FabFilter 102

FabFilter Creative Bundle Explored

FabFilter are well known for their mixing plugins, but they also have some hidden gems in their creative bundle. Trainer and sound designer Rishabh Rajan created this course to show you all about them. Lets get creative!

EZ Drummer 3 101

EZ Drummer Explored

If you're a music producer or sound engineer looking to create realistic drum tracks without needing a professional drummer, Toontrack's EZ Drummer 3 is the perfect solution. Discover how to make the most of this drum production software in this course, led by trainer and multi-instrumentalist Matt Vanacoro!

Ableton Live 406

Granulator Explored

Granulator II is a powerful Max for Live device included in Ableton Live Suite. This course, led by Ableton Certified Trainer Thavius Beck, will help you learn Granulator to create anything from lush soundscapes to glitchy effects, and other interesting sonic textures.

Omnisphere 301

Omnisphere Advanced Sound Design

Are you using Spectrasonics Omnisphere and only taking advantage of its presets? Don't miss out on the wealth of creative possibilities! Watch this course to learn how to use this powerful instrument to its fullest with sound designer Rishabh Rajan.

Freeform 101

Freeform Productivity Explored

Freeform is Apple's new app that makes brainstorming and project planning easy and fun. Learn to turn your creative ideas into reality, with this course by trainer and Apple expert Matt Vanacoro. See where your imagination will take you...

FL Studio 100

21 Hot New Features in FL Studio 21

FL Studio 21 is loaded with new plugins, workflow improvements and more... Make sure to grab a cold drink, because you're about to discover 21 HOT new features in FL Studio 21, with trainer and producer Rishabh Rajan!

Polyend Play 101

Polyend Play Beginner's Guide

Are you ready to unlock the full potential of Polyend's Play? Join music producer and trainer Thavius Beck in this exciting course as he expertly guides you through every feature of this one-of-a-kind groovebox. Let's Play!

iZotope RX

RX 10 Video Manual

iZotope's RX 10 is a powerful but complex audio repair toolkit. No need to read the fine manual... Check out this RX 10 Video Manual by audio expert Joe Albano and learn to turn your imperfect audio into pristine recording faster than you can say "RX"!

Bitwig Studio 403

Track Deconstruction: The Big Round Table

Would you like to watch Bitwig Certified Pro Thavius Beck deconstruct his latest track? We did! And that's why we commissioned this deep dive course into the making of his new EP tune "The Big Round Table". You're just one click away from some very cool tips and tricks!
